    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, meticulously maintained to preserve its peak mechanical integrity. This example features the celebrated S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. The high-revving powerplant is paired with a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive Vanos system overhaul, rod bearing replacement with VAC coated shells, and documented rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with fresh bushings throughout, ensuring the razor-sharp handling characteristics this chassis is known for. The exterior finish retains its original luster with zero oxidation, and the interior remains a time capsule of Nappa leather and tactile precision. A truly turn-key enthusiast machine with no deferred maintenance.",
